Nashua.Killicut-Way House: The Killicut-Way House is a historic house at 2 Old House Lane (a stub roadway containing just this house at the end of Tempo Drive) in Nashua, New Hampshire. Estimated to have been built c. 1740, this 1-1/2 story Cape style house is one of the oldest buildings in Nashua, and one of a small number of houses from that period in the region that is relatively unaltered.
